name: WOMENS MUSIC MAKES HIGH TEE
description:
Music is a reason to get out of bed in the morning. Listen to it, dance to it, act crazy and tap your foot to a different beat. Express your passion for sound with this item and let music make you high.

COLOR: Iris

4.1 oz., 100% combed ringspun cotton. Perfect fit. Set-in 1x1 collar. Tapered waist. Coverstitching on collar, shoulders, and arm openings. Sideseamed. Set-in sleeves. Garment washed. No shrinkage.
